snippet.title: Skorecery - Original Release Date Trailer [DELAYED]
snippet.description:
UPDATE 2: The new release date is April 4th 2019 on PS4! Check out the latest release date trailer here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yE1pECt_4RI

UPDATE: Unfortunately the game was delayed beyond this original Feb 5th date. 

Skorecery is a fast-paced, mystical, local multiplayer PS4 title that's coming February 5th 2019!
Learn more at http://skorecery.com
Follow at https://twitter.com/skorecery

Not all images are representative of the final game
